General.Name: Domec Compania de Artefactos Domesticos SAIC y F
General.Description: DOMEC Compañía de Artefactos Domésticos S.A.I.C.y F. engages in the manufacture and sale of appliances for domestic use, gas appliances, and electric refrigeration in Argentina. It provides gastronomic type line, ovens, stoves, cooktops, purifiers, and bells. The company was founded in 1948 and is based in Buenos Aires, Argentina.
